AFK Katas Home Personal Commission MIOBC HS Teach MIT I collected these katas and grapples intially to help me remember all the details  and later to help me and my boys prepare for the black belt test  I hope they can help others affiliated with the American Freestyle Karate studio in their path to black belt also  They are written in  chunks  to help make memorizing them easier  They are all in pdf form so you can print them out or save them  Please let me know of any errors you find  Katas Basic Kata 1 Universal Kata Elbow Sequence Star Form Moon Form Bo Kata Kama Kata Chase Self Defenses Self defenses at the Kyu levels are against both punches and knives  Inside Blocks   rotation 1 Palm Heels   rotation 2 Knife Hands   rotation 3 Knife Hands   Preblack  all rotations 